Title: Lorentz violation and the proper-time method
Authors: T. Mariz and J. R. Nascimento and A. Yu. Petrov and L. Y. Santos and A. J. da Silva
Abstract: In this paper, we apply the proper-time method to generate the Lorentz-violating Chern-Simons terms in the four-dimensional Yang-Mills and non-linearized gravity theories. It is shown that the coefficient of the induced Chern-Simons term is finite but regularization dependent.
